item.title: HTB: Meow
item.description: Introduction I was successful in completing my first HackTheBox machine, by the name of “Meow”. This was a great introduction, as it allowed me to acclimatise to these machines and to understand how they function. In order for me to hack these boxes, I will be utilising my own personal machine, which is running Parrot OS on VMware. Before we begin to hack this machine, we must first answer a couple of questions.
